      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RING A HOUDINI (8) has a strong record this track and trip with eight wins and five placings from 20 starts. Below best last time at Warragul (26.68) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length fourth. Looks a key chance on best form. CRUELLA (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4 lengths (19.94) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. One of the better hopes. SAILPLANE (7) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a long neck at this track in a handy 19.65 beating Tropic Man. Must be included in calculations. ZIPPI MUSTANG (6) is a last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
